creator: Web Freeze Solution
descriptionHtml:
My Price List is a simple solution for creating product price list for shopkeepers, retail, service and wholesale business.

In essence, a price list gives you a clear picture of cost price and sale price of the products. You can quick overview the price of your products in a tap.

My Price List can store unlimited products and creates price lists an efficient and productive part of your product sales and marketing.

My Price List has very handy and user friendly interface which is built on Native Android Technology to give you the best experience.


FEATURES:

- A price list includes Product Name, Size/Weight, Quantity, Cost Price, Sale Price, Category, Barcode and Photo

- Built-in Barcode (UPC Code) scanner

- Linear structure and visually clean product list to highlight product's detail

- Backup and Restore products to multiple devices

- Generate PDF and XLS (Excel) file to share and print

- Tap to quick view, Hold to quick edit

- Can store unlimited products

- Manage categories easily

- Add, edit, delete or share product in a few taps

- Option to change currency country-wise

- Quick product search

- Built on Native Android Technology for best user experience


NOTE: The default 4 digits PIN for 'Delete All' option is 1234.
descriptionShort: Price list maker for shopkeepers and service providers

title: Make Price List & Invoice

creator: Web Freeze Solution
descriptionHtml:
Make Price List is a simple, fast and easy solution for creating item price lists and invoices for shopkeepers, retail, service and wholesale business.

In essence, a price list gives you a clear picture of cost price and sale price of the items. You can quickly overview the price of your items in a tap.

Make Price List can store unlimited items and creates price lists & invoices, an efficient and productive part of your item sales and marketing.


Key Features:

- A price list includes Item Name, Size/Weight, Quantity, Cost Price, Sale Price, Category, Barcode/QR code and Photo

- Generate invoices that you can print and download as PDF

- Built-in Barcode/QR code (UPC Code) scanner

- Linear structure and visually clean items list to highlight item details

- Backup and Restore items to multiple devices

- Generate PDF and XLSX (Excel) file to share and print

- Can store unlimited items and invoices

- Manage categories easily

- Add, edit, delete or share item in a few taps

- Option to change currency country-wise

- Quick item search with Barcode/QR code scanner


Reason to choose Make Price List:

Make Price List has a very handy and user friendly interface which gives you the best experience and provides you a clear picture of cost and sale price of the items.
descriptionShort: Price list and invoice maker for shopkeepers and service providers

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
- Now you can import data from XLS, XLSX or CSV file and export it in XLSX or PDF format
- Added scanner option to search items while creating or editing invoice
- Added new currency Malawi Kwacha (MK)
